overview: The user tasked the agent with comprehensive browser-based testing of
  the application. The agent began by verifying the dev server and navigating
  the main questionnaire. It successfully tested the "Pre-fill & Jump to Report"
  functionality, confirming the report section and PDF download. For the admin
  dashboard, after being redirected to the login page, the agent tested the
  error handling with an incorrect password, confirming its functionality.
  During manual questionnaire navigation, the agent observed conditional fields
  working correctly and confirmed that form validation was handled by the API,
  not section-by-section navigation. Finally, API endpoints for responses were
  tested, confirming authentication requirements and robust data validation. The
  overall testing confirmed the application's core functionalities and security
  measures.
